OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with patchy rain,
OL,6,Fclearing eastwards during the morning,
OL,7,Fsunny spells developing during the
OL,8,Fafternoon. More seasonable
OL,9,Ftemperatures expected. Winds moderate
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly, breezy along the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FClearing skies during the
OL,13,Fevening with light winds will see
OL,14,Fovernight temperatures dropping and
OL,15,Ffeeling cooler than of late. Cloud
OL,16,Fspreading eastwards by the morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
