OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA cloudy with some sunny
OL,6,Fintervals developing during the day,
OL,7,Fclouding over during the evening with
OL,8,Fshowers overnight some of which could
OL,9,Fbe heavy or even Thundery.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FTurning more unsettled on Tuesday with
OL,13,Fsunshine and showers. Wednesday starts
OL,14,Foff sunny, then clouding over with
OL,15,Frain later. A wet start on Thursday
OL,16,Fbefore cloud clearing and becoming
OL,17,Fsunny.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
